For all queries on the data analyses presented in this document, please contact the author.

Total Abundance Birds - AIC and best models

# fit each univariate model, plus the intercept-only.

fitList <- list(
"Intercept-only"          = glm.nb(Total_Abundance ~ 1,                                         data = bird),
"med_inc"                 = glm.nb(Total_Abundance ~ med_inc,                                   data = bird),
"park.size_km"            = glm.nb(Total_Abundance ~ park.size_km,                              data = bird),
"dist.to.nat.km"          = glm.nb(Total_Abundance ~ dist.to.nat.km,                            data = bird),   
"within.prop.imperv"      = glm.nb(Total_Abundance ~ within.prop.imperv,                        data = bird),   
"within.prop.trees"       = glm.nb(Total_Abundance ~ within.prop.trees,                         data = bird),   
"within.prop.grass"       = glm.nb(Total_Abundance ~ within.prop.grass,                         data = bird),
"within.prop.bare"        = glm.nb(Total_Abundance ~ within.prop.bare,                          data = bird),
"surround.prop.imperv"    = glm.nb(Total_Abundance ~ surround.prop.imperv,                      data = bird),   
"surround.prop.trees"     = glm.nb(Total_Abundance ~ surround.prop.trees,                       data = bird),   
"surround.prop.grass"     = glm.nb(Total_Abundance ~ surround.prop.grass,                       data = bird),
"surround.prop.bare"      = glm.nb(Total_Abundance ~ surround.prop.bare,                        data = bird)
)

#fit the ggplot

f1 <- ggplot(bird,
                aes(within.prop.bare,
                    Total_Abundance)) +
  theme_classic() + 
  
  geom_smooth(method = "glm.nb", 
              alpha= I(0.3),
              fill="slategray",
              fullrange = TRUE) +
  
  stat_smooth(geom="line",
              method = "glm.nb", 
              alpha= I(0.5),
              size=2,
              color="gray12",
              fullrange = TRUE) +
  
  geom_point(aes(colour = Park_Needs_modified),
             alpha = I(0.8),
             size = 4,
             position = position_jitter(height = 0.02, width = 0)) +
  
  scale_colour_manual(breaks = c("High", "Moderate", "Low"),
                      values=c("High" = "darkblue", "Moderate" = "goldenrod3", "Low" = "firebrick4")) +
  
  theme(axis.title.y = element_text(size = rel(1), family="sans", angle = 90), axis.text.y  = element_text(vjust=1.5, size=12, family="sans")) + 
  
  theme(axis.title.x = element_text(size = rel(1), family="sans"), axis.text.x  = element_text(vjust=1.5, size=10, family="sans")) + 
  
  theme(legend.position = "bottom") +
  
    labs(x="within.prop.bare", 
       y = "Total_Abundance") +
  
  theme(text = element_text(size=12))
